== 背景 ==
2018年9月，[[俄羅斯自由民主黨|俄羅斯自由民主黨]]候選人[[謝爾蓋·富爾加爾|謝爾蓋·富爾加爾]]在{{link-en|2018年哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區區長選舉|2018 Khabarovsk Krai gubernatorial election|哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區區長選舉}}中擊敗執政黨[[統一俄羅斯|統一俄羅斯]]候選人[[維亞切斯拉夫·什波特|維亞切斯拉夫·什波特]]，成為當地新任首長<ref name="worldjournal-2020-07-13">{{cite news | url=https://www.worldjournal.com/7042203/article-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%81%A0%E6%9D%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%A6%96%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4/ | title=俄羅斯遠東地區首長被捕自稱無罪 民眾上街聲援 | publisher=世界日報 | date=2020-07-13 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716211700/https://www.worldjournal.com/7042203/article-%e4%bf%84%e7%be%85%e6%96%af%e9%81%a0%e6%9d%b1%e5%9c%b0%e5%8d%80%e9%a6%96%e9%95%b7%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e8%87%aa%e7%a8%b1%e7%84%a1%e7%bd%aa-%e6%b0%91%e7%9c%be%e4%b8%8a%e8%a1%97%e8%81%b2%e6%8f%b4/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Фургал вступил в должность губернатора Хабаровского края | url=https://www.gazeta.ru/politics/news/2018/09/28/n_12097549.shtml | website=gazeta.ru | language=ru | date=2018-09-18 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711202243/https://www.gazeta.ru/politics/news/2018/09/28/n_12097549.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據[[金融時報_(英國)|金融時報]]的報道，有市民稱投票予富爾加爾是因為想對抗統一俄羅斯的當權者。<ref>{{cite news | language=en-GB | title=Protesting Putin: Kremlin faces revolt in the regions | url=https://www.ft.com/content/a66161bf-a136-4329-91ec-c194570b6784?commentID=6d2c75d4-6c04-4798-878b-4568fbd91193 | work=[[金融時報_(英國)|金融時報 (英國)]] | date=2020-08-06 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123704/https://www.ft.com/content/a66161bf-a136-4329-91ec-c194570b6784?commentID=6d2c75d4-6c04-4798-878b-4568fbd91193 | dead-url=no }}</ref>同年12月，俄羅斯總統普丁宣佈將[[遠東聯邦管區|遠東聯邦管區]]的行政中心由[[伯力|伯力]]遷往[[海參崴|海參崴]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://meduza.io/news/2018/12/13/putin-perenes-stolitsu-dalnevostochnogo-federalnogo-okruga-vo-vladivostok | title=Путин перенес столицу Дальневосточного федерального округа во Владивосток | language=ru | website=meduza.io | date=2018-12-13 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2019-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402080252/https://meduza.io/news/2018/12/13/putin-perenes-stolitsu-dalnevostochnogo-federalnogo-okruga-vo-vladivostok | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年9月的[[哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區杜馬|哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區杜馬]]選舉中，俄羅斯自民黨贏得多數議席，重挫執政黨。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://vostokmedia.com/news/politics/09-09-2019/ldpr-stala-partiey-vlasti-v-habarovskom-krae | title=ЛДПР стала «партией власти» в Хабаровском крае | publisher=Vostok Media | language=ru | date=2019-09-09 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711172611/https://vostokmedia.com/news/politics/09-09-2019/ldpr-stala-partiey-vlasti-v-habarovskom-krae | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年6月25日至7月1日，俄羅斯舉行[[2020年俄羅斯修憲公投|修憲公投]]<ref>{{cite news | url=https://meduza.io/en/feature/2020/06/12/look-after-yourself-vote-electronically | title=‘Look after yourself — vote electronically!’ Moscow’s civil servants report being forced to register for online voting ahead of Russia’s constitutional plebiscite | publisher=meduza.io | language=en | date=2020-06-13 | access-date=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-07-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701165052/https://meduza.io/en/feature/2020/06/12/look-after-yourself-vote-electronically | dead-url=no }}</ref>，通過令總統普丁可以掌權至2036年<ref name="worldjournal-2020-07-13" />。幾天後的7月9日，富爾加爾便被[[俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會|俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會]]逮捕並送到離哈巴羅夫斯克地區幾千公里的[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]監禁，指控他與2004至2005年期間幾宗謀殺案有關，他否認指控。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/09/local-russian-governor-sergei-furgal-arrested-over-multiple-charges | title=Russian provincial governor arrested over killings of business rivals | language=en-GB | publisher=衛報 | date=2020-07-09 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123715/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/09/local-russian-governor-sergei-furgal-arrested-over-multiple-charges | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.voacantonese.com/a/Russian-far-east-anti-kremlin-protests-continue-20200809/5536414.html | title=俄羅斯遠東地區反克里姆林宮抗議在繼續 | language=zh | publisher=美國之音 | date=2020-08-09 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123728/https://www.voacantonese.com/a/Russian-far-east-anti-kremlin-protests-continue-20200809/5536414.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>根據，俄羅斯自由民主黨主席[[弗拉基米尔·沃尔福维奇·日里诺夫斯基|日里诺夫斯基]]在講話中指會以全部自民黨成員辭職，回應這個「不公平」的案件，又稱要讓全世界知道這個國家的混亂，質疑是甚麼原因使富爾加爾因為多年前的「罪行」而被捕，揣測稱他或許是沒有「把錢送到莫斯科」。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://meduza.io/en/news/2020/07/09/in-fiery-speech-in-russian-parliament-vladimir-zhirinovsky-condemns-arrest-of-khabarovsk-governor-threatens-mass-resignations-and-even-revolution-in-response | title=In fiery speech in Russian Parliament, Vladimir Zhirinovsky condemns arrest of Khabarovsk governor, threatens mass resignations and even ‘revolution’ in response | language=en | publisher=meduza.io | date=2020-07-09 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716021608/https://meduza.io/en/news/2020/07/09/in-fiery-speech-in-russian-parliament-vladimir-zhirinovsky-condemns-arrest-of-khabarovsk-governor-threatens-mass-resignations-and-even-revolution-in-response | dead-url=no }}</ref>他承諾會為富爾加爾爭取赦免。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.mk.ru/incident/2020/07/23/zhirinovskiy-rasskazal-o-budushhem-furgala.html | title=Жириновский рассказал о будущем Фургала | language=ru | publisher=mk.ru | date=2020-07-23 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-08-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802190902/https://www.mk.ru/incident/2020/07/23/zhirinovskiy-rasskazal-o-budushhem-furgala.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 過程 ==
7月11日，[[哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區|哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區]]首府城市[[伯力|伯力]]有大批市民上街示威，[[俄羅斯聯邦內務部|內務部]]預測指有1萬至1萬2千人參與<ref name="meduza-io-2020-07-11" /><ref name="tass-ru-2020-07-12" />，《[[生意人報|生意人報]]》則報道稱有3萬至3萬5千人參與示威活動<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/4415230 | language=ru | title=Акция протеста против ареста Фургала стала самой массовой в истории Хабаровска | website=kommersant.ru | date=2020-07-11 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729155548/https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/4415230 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在集會中當地警察沒有介入或干涉集會，反而向示威群眾派發口罩，示威者則感謝警察，產生了有趣的互動。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%81%A0%E6%9D%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%A6%96%E9%95%B7-%E9%AB%98%E5%96%8A-%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E6%98%AF%E8%B3%8A/ | title=俄羅斯遠東地區數萬人上街示威　聲援被捕地區首長　高喊「普京是賊」 | date=2020-07-19 | work=立場新聞 | language=zh-HK | access-date=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123801/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%81%A0%E6%9D%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%A6%96%E9%95%B7-%E9%AB%98%E5%96%8A-%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E6%98%AF%E8%B3%8A/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:Demonstration_in_support_of_Governor_Sergey_Furgal_in_Khabarovsk,_12_July_2020,_night-1.jpg|thumb]]
7月12日，當地有數百名市民上街示威，穿越市中心遊行至政府總部，聲援被捕的[[謝爾蓋·富爾加爾|富爾加爾]]<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2071779 | title=俄遠東地區首長被捕自稱無罪 民眾上街聲援 | publisher=中央廣播電臺 | language=zh-TW | date=2020-07-12 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730052324/https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2071779 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一方面，俄羅斯副總理兼遠東聯邦管區全權代表[[尤里·彼得羅維奇·特魯特涅夫|尤里·特魯特涅夫]]抵達伯力，「評估」指當地的領導為差劣。<ref>{{cite web | author= | url=https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/4415814 | title=Трутнев заявил о плохой работе властей Хабаровского края | language=ru | website=kommersant.ru | publisher= | date= | accessdate= | archive-date=2020-08-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817152307/https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/4415814 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月16日，富爾加爾的代表律師表示富爾加爾感謝群眾支持，但不認同民眾違法地上街示威。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53437595 | title=俄羅斯伯力示威：群眾抗議莫斯科抓捕受歡迎首長　遠東響起反普京口號 | publisher=BBC中文 | language=zh-hant | date=2020-07-16 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123812/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53437595 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月18日，再有高達五萬名市民參與伯力的示威抗議活動，哈巴羅夫斯克邊疆區其他城市亦有相應的示威活動<ref>{{cite news | url=https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4713881 | title=俄遠東首長因故被捕 居民不滿爆抗議 | language=zh-TW | work=台灣醒報 | publisher=聯合新聞網 | author=施凱文 | date=2020-07-19 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725095929/https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4713881 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[阿穆爾河畔共青城|阿穆爾河畔共青城]]有約1千人上街表示對富爾加爾的支持。此外，在[[濱海邊疆區|濱海邊疆區]]首府[[海參崴|海參崴]]亦有數以百計的民眾上街示威，當中兩名示威者被捕。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://meduza.io/feature/2020/07/18/v-habarovske-desyatki-tysyach-chelovek-vyshli-na-aktsii-v-podderzhku-sergeya-furgala-glavnoe | title=В Хабаровске десятки тысяч человек вышли на акцию в поддержку Сергея Фургала. Главное | website=meduza.io | date=2020-07-18 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-07-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730000930/https://meduza.io/feature/2020/07/18/v-habarovske-desyatki-tysyach-chelovek-vyshli-na-aktsii-v-podderzhku-sergeya-furgala-glavnoe | dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月20日，總統普丁正式宣佈解任富爾加爾作為邊疆區首長的職務，委任一名來自[[薩馬拉|薩馬拉]]的自由民主黨國家杜馬議員[[米哈伊尔·弗拉基米罗维奇·杰格佳廖夫|米哈伊尔·杰格佳廖夫]]作為區首長，並指他將代理區長職務直至第二年的選舉，然而，杰格佳廖夫抵達伯力後惹來更大的反彈，批評他沒有經驗和與地區沒有聯繫。<ref name="standnews-2020-07-26">{{Cite web | url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%81%A0%E6%9D%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E5%8D%80%E9%95%B7/ | title=俄羅斯遠東城市連續三星期反普京示威　數萬人抗議當局以政治動機拘捕區長 | language=zh-HK | date=2020-07-26 | work=立場新聞 | access-date=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123757/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%81%A0%E6%9D%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E5%8D%80%E9%95%B7/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kremlin.ru/events/president/news/63689 | title=Михаил Дегтярёв назначен врио губернатора Хабаровского края | language=ru | publisher=kremlin.ru | date=2020-07-20 | access-date=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-08-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804081015/http://kremlin.ru/events/president/news/63689 | dead-url=no }}</ref>杰格佳廖夫在第二天的記者會中指，他不是想要與富爾加爾作對，若富爾加爾希望再次成為區長，他便會「回到莫斯科」<ref>{{cite news | url=https://ria.ru/20200721/1574657848.html | title=Дегтярев оценил перспективы участия на выборах главы Хабаровского края | publisher=ria.ru | language=ru | date=2020-07-21 | access-date=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-07-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731105303/https://ria.ru/20200721/1574657848.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7月21日，兩名哈巴羅夫斯克地區議員宣佈退出俄羅斯自由民主黨，抗議莫斯科政府拘捕富爾加爾的行動。<ref>{{cite news | title=Anti-Putin Protests in Russia's Far East Gather Steam | url=https://www.voanews.com/east-asia-pacific/anti-putin-protests-russias-far-east-gather-steam | language=en | publisher=美國之音 | date=2020-07-25 | access-date=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-08-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806072808/https://www.voanews.com/east-asia-pacific/anti-putin-protests-russias-far-east-gather-steam | dead-url=no }}</ref>

